      • ModDashTab

        public ModDashTab​(String name,
                  NetworkTable table)
        Create a new ModDash Tab. USE ModDash.getTab(String); Certain features will not work otherwise.
        Parameters:
        name - the unique string name of this tab
        table - the NetworkTables subtable that corresponds to this tab.
